	  DDDDaaaayyyy,	TTTTiiiimmmmoooo HHHHaaaakkkkuuuulllliiiinnnneeeennnn,	SSSStttteeeevvvveeee LLLLiiiinnnnhhhhaaaarrrrtttt, DDDDeeeeaaaannnn LLLLuuuuiiiicccckkkk, PPPPaaaatttt RRRRaaaannnnkkkkiiiinnnn, EEEErrrriiiicccc
