	  EEEEnnnnggggbbbbeeeerrrr,  DDDDaaaavvvviiiidddd  HHHHaaaaiiiirrrrssssttttoooonnnn, MMMMiiiicccchhhhaaaaeeeellll HHHHaaaammmmeeeellll, JJJJoooonnnnaaaatttthhhhaaaannnn HHHHaaaannnnddddlllleeeerrrr, JJJJoooohhhhnnnnnnnnyyyy
	  LLLLeeeeeeee, TTTTiiiimmmm LLLLeeeennnnnnnnaaaannnn, RRRRoooobbbb MMMMeeeennnnkkkkeeee, and AAAAnnnnddddyyyy SSSSwwwwaaaannnnssssoooonnnn,	 developed  NetHack
