	       TTTTiiiimmmmoooo HHHHaaaakkkkuuuulllliiiinnnneeeennnn ported NetHack 3.1 to OS/2.  EEEErrrriiiicccc	SSSSmmmmiiiitttthhhh port-
	  ed  NetHack  3.1 to the Atari.  PPPPaaaatttt RRRRaaaannnnkkkkiiiinnnn, with help	from JJJJoooosssshhhhuuuuaaaa
	  DDDDeeeellllaaaahhhhuuuunnnnttttyyyy, is	responsible for	the VMS	 version  of  NetHack  3.1.
	  MMMMiiiicccchhhhaaaaeeeellll AAAAlllllllliiiissssoooonnnn ported NetHack 3.1 to	Windows	NT.

	       DDDDeeeeaaaannnn LLLLuuuuiiiicccckkkk, with	help from DDDDaaaavvvviiiidddd	 CCCCoooohhhhrrrrssss,	 developed  NetHack
	  3.1 for X11.


